---
title: Balsamic Rosemary Pork Chops with Garlic Herb Toast & Roasted Green Beans
description: Over here, we believe pork chops are a canvas, and we like to paint them with allllll the flavors. Tonight’s palette: A saucy coating that includes fresh rosemary, tangy balsamic vinegar, and creamy garlic herb butter—because why choose one of these ingredients when you could have them all? Add to that a side of garlic herb toast and tender roasted green beans, and you have yourself a dinner to Remem-brandt (see what we did there?).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61cb2476d71940215d37063e-e8f41a59.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/balsamic-rosemary-pork-chops-61cb2476d71940215d37063e-93d1ad73.pdf
